{"tid":379062,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[工程] 畢業入大公司定細公司，已經決定左你人生既 99%","createTime":"2017-08-29T03:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T13:01:14.000Z","uid":14170,"like":117,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aee852e4c8a44087b9798976aa387a5cd03a4ddd","tid":379062,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:24:59.000Z","msg":"理論上大公司頭兩年學唔到實際野，搞下公司活動練下吹水 present &amp; 領導能力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相反，細公司落地盤「相信」會學到好多實際野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大公司兩年 GE training 乜都學唔到，完左仲係 on99 拎 30K <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細公司完 Scheme 岩岩好 20K，少 10K 但地盤真男人經驗係無價 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大公司六年考到 MHKIE 註冊工程師資格 40K <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細公司辛苦左六年 25K，諗緊幾時先考牌好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大公司十年已經上到 Project Manager 負責幾單 Project 睇進度，一唔岩就屌人唔洗比面人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細公司十年仲係 Senior Engineer，考牌衰左已經無諗住 Charter，老細尋日比 Client 屌到一面屁，返到黎又搵你出氣，對工程行業無哂興趣唔想再做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大公司十五年，生左個女後重視 work life balance，早收工返屋企幫個女溫書！<br />\n細公司十五年，女朋友都未搵到，日日早返遲放做到想跳樓"},{"pid":"ddcf0ce95e480313a19152de24570d8b93f4b110","tid":379062,"uid":7796,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:27:14.000Z","msg":"又寫得幾好"},{"pid":"001a78a3db925e500a49b5cf95078a68de6c5821","tid":379062,"uid":14170,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:35:10.000Z","msg":"大公司二十年，做左 FHKIE 算係業界幾有影響力既人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時做下訪問叫年青人入行投身工程界<br />\n細公司二十年，終於追到 40K，忙到仆街之餘仲周身病痛，生活就係 返工 睇醫生 訓教，得閒上下連登踩下工程唱臭呢行"},{"pid":"b0607c41be81abc44c028de7c610695d64ecffb3","tid":379062,"uid":10171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:37:57.000Z","msg":"又話自己做sub仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9855465a2e3e2fa85e217317988dc91784edcf36","tid":379062,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:39:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又話自己做sub仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認命 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a9365c98dcc3211339369a35047f2b846bfcb3","tid":379062,"uid":14170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:44:03.000Z","msg":"各位師弟要努力讀書，take 多啲 presentation 既科，好好訓練語文能力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8d05d10d73c8fe38341d37ec00726e261a86a0","tid":379062,"uid":25753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:45:58.000Z","msg":"做得細公司 真係成世做細公司咩"},{"pid":"9ac27f9dbd2bac7dd9c77b29726c281da1993b76","tid":379062,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:47:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做得細公司 真係成世做細公司咩</blockquote><br />\n大公司 GE = 親生仔，細公司就算當你好西利萬中無一跳到入大公司，待遇都差天共地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c215083f9c096093e18a36059402855692c1ed","tid":379062,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:52:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做得細公司 真係成世做細公司咩</blockquote><br />\n大公司 GE = 親生仔，細公司就算當你好西利萬中無一跳到入大公司，待遇都差天共地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好諗住靠咩地盤經驗實力跳入大公司，然後平步青雲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大公司根本唔重視呢啲野，大公司講既係 title &amp; 個人魅力，要經驗咪請間有經驗既 main con 做單 project"},{"pid":"94bea323f37b05c895ee09bdede016c80340c66b","tid":379062,"uid":37501,"lik